						<div class="postbody">As badly mistuned as the DPCM channel is, there are still some rates that are compatible with each other. Unfortunately, it's mostly the slower sample rates.<br /><br />I made a <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/User:Lidnariq/DPCM_mistuning" class="postlink">table about it on the wiki</a>.</div>

