						<div class="postbody">It's DPCM (Famitracker doesn't do PCM), it's the last track of the NSF (51), and it's the classic fairlight &quot;orch5&quot; sample. It's not particularly well made as a DPCM sample either; there's a nasty pop on the end. As I said, I think it's just there for a laugh. I don't think it was even included in the bandcamp soundtrack.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

